Choose the payment method and fill in the data. If the payer fails to receive confirmation, he/she receives a full refund (100%%) of the amount paid. If a beauty seeker has paid for a beauty service, which has been confirmed, and he/she misses the appointment with the beauty service provider, the refund will be determined by the cancellation policy set by the beauty service provider.

1. How do I register on the website?

Click on your desired listing and select time and date from the right panel, then click the blue button "Book now"

source: 5. How do I change the location where I want to find beauty services?
